DESCRIPTION:
Why this property?

This is the finest plot in prasanth nagar, ideal for peaceful living, future investment, or rental income. Rare to find such properties in a premium neighborhood with two-Side road access and abundant space.

Square corner plot with road on two sides, just opposite to children's park and 50 meters distance to cricket/ foot ball ground. The most prime property in prasanth nagar with enough space to park 4 cars. Corner plot with no house es on the eastern side of the plot, the land is always filled with cool breeze with good air circulation especially coming from the east side of the plot. Large open space on the eastern side, enjoy natural ventilation and cool breeze all day.

The property is located just 3 kms proximity to medical college, sree chitra institute of medical sciences, regional cancer center, only 6 kms to lullu mall, 3 kms to aakkulam boat house, 8 kms to technopark, 8 kms to railway station, 9 kms to international airport. Major malls, shopping centers, government offices are all located within 10 kms vicinity of the property.

House is well maintained and many modifications and changes made in the previous years. 24x7 water supply is available with 2 tanks of 1000 litres each on the ground floor and 1000 litres and 500 litres tank on the terrace.

The house and land is the most ideal place for people to enjoy a serene peaceful atmosphere and relax, tranquil and noise free environmental, ideal for professionals with tight work schedules to relax and enjoy the natural environment and for families and retired persons too. The plot is very ideal for doctors especially who have a large client base as there is too much space available for parking and enough space to build a separate consultation room.
